@ChelseaFC to face @dynamokyiven in round of 16 of the @EuropaLeague, with first tie at Stamford Bridge on Thursday 7 March.<br />
<br />
14 March: Second leg

In an interview in August by @DavidWalshST with Britain&rsquo;s wealthiest citizen Jim Ratcliffe, he refused to comment on whether he was/interested in buying Chelsea FC, but his comments are very interesting.. <br />
<br />
&rdquo;You&rsquo;ve only got two [top-drawer] footballers at Chelsea, Hazard and Kante. So you need to strengthen the team a little. You&rsquo;ve got two fabulous players but the numbers don&rsquo;t work. If you buy the club you want to spend some money on players. Otherwise you end up being Arsenal.&rdquo;

